{
  "id": "RAW_33ff4698",
  "title": "终于！React 又发新版本了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==&mid=2247535903&idx=1&sn=2e3cc42ac7927f10e54b9801232c00d5",
  "date": "2025-10-02 03:27:00",
  "author": "前端充电宝",
  "siteName": "前端充电宝",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c256fdae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FEO58xpw5UMOt86icUhkTwcOxnuwxzZ4NEGpWmmU2APpT0jF6zOkeLwzyGZkG7nEAgbtwJGXnCTc53wTjXQmPtJA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <div data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"word-wrap:break-word;overflow:hidden;font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;font-family:'PingFang SC', 'SF Pro Text', 'Microsoft YaHei', sans-serif;\">\n    <div style=\"height: auto;\">\n     <div>\n      <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"前端充电宝\" data-alias=\"FE-Charge\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/EO58xpw5UMNJLOYUj7Uv3TSiaqDldeaxxhCosR00yDKGR9lvI4y9NOfG7ADJHfKEsKuVAFWgDPqLN5afgZGkbZg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"聚焦前端开发，探索AI新浪潮：宝藏工具×前沿动态×实战技巧，解锁前端新可能！\" data-id=\"MzU2MTIyNDUwMA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这几年，前端两大框架 React 和 Vue 都进入了一个相对稳定的阶段。版本更新不再像早期那样频繁“放大招”，而是更多地在打磨细节、优化体验。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">尤其是 React，自从 v17 之后，新功能更偏向“锦上添花”。今年三月底，React 发布了 v19.1。半年后，10 月 1 日，React 团队又带来了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">React 19.2</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">虽然这是一次小迭代，但里面的几个新特性都很实用，尤其对&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">复杂交互、性能优化、以及服务端渲染（SSR）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;场景有不少帮助。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面我们一起来看看。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">&lt;Activity&gt;：一键“冻结”与“解冻”</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">有没有遇到过这种情况：</span></p>\n      <blockquote style=\"margin-top: 16px;font-style: italic;margin: 20px 0;padding: 12px 20px;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.04);border-left: 4px solid #0066ff;border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-top: 0;margin: 0;color: #4e5969;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户离开了一个复杂的组件（例如一个带着大量输入的表单），等再回来时，却发现状态丢了，必须重新填？</span></p>\n      </blockquote>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前我们可能需要写一堆缓存逻辑。现在，React 提供了官方的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">&lt;Activity /&gt;</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;组件来解决这个问题。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">它有两个模式：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">visible</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：正常渲染，组件照常工作；</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">hidden</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：组件隐藏，同时卸载副作用、暂停更新，但会保留状态。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当你切回&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">visible</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;时，组件能瞬间恢复之前的状态，像是“解冻”一样。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这对&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">路由切换、多标签应用、抽屉式导航</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;特别有用。比如你打开一个设置面板，切到别的页面，再回来时面板还能保持原样，体验会非常丝滑。</span></p>\n      <pre style=\"border-radius:6px 12px 6px 12px;border:1px solid #ebedf0;padding:16px;margin:16px 0;font-size:0.8em;overflow-x:auto;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;line-height:1.6;\" tabindex=\"0\"><code style=\"border:none;padding:0;white-space:nowrap;display:block;\"><span line=\"1\"><span><span leaf=\"\">import</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;useState&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;from</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">react</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">;</span></span></span><span line=\"2\"><span><span leaf=\"\">import</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Activity&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;from</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">react</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">;</span></span></span><span line=\"4\"><span><span leaf=\"\">function</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;TabPanel</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">({</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;children</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;isActive&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">})</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span></span><span line=\"5\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; return</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;(</span></span></span><span line=\"6\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">Activity</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;mode</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">={</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">isActive</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;?&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">visible</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;:&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">hidden</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">}&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"7\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; {</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">children</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span></span><span line=\"8\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">Activity</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"9\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; );</span></span></span><span line=\"10\"><span><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span></span><span line=\"12\"><span><span leaf=\"\">function</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;App</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">()</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span></span><span line=\"13\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; const</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;[</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">active</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;setActive</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">]</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;=</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;useState</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">profile</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">);</span></span></span><span line=\"15\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; return</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;(</span></span></span><span line=\"16\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">div</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"17\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">button</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;onClick</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">={() =&gt;&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">setActive</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">profile</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">)}&gt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">个人资料</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&lt;/</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">button</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"18\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">button</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;onClick</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">={() =&gt;&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">setActive</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">settings</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">)}&gt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">设置</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&lt;/</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">button</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"20\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">TabPanel</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;isActive</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">={</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">active</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;===&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">profile</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">}&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"21\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">ProfileForm</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"22\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">TabPanel</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"23\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">TabPanel</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;isActive</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">={</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">active</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;===&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">settings</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">}&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"24\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">SettingsList</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;/&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"25\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">TabPanel</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"26\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">div</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"27\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; );</span></span></span><span line=\"28\"><span><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">👉 常见用途：页面预加载、表单保留、切换时后台准备数据。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">useEffectEvent：告别依赖陷阱</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">React 里的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">useEffect</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;经常让人头大：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">回调一旦依赖 props 或 state，就容易导致 Effect 重复执行；</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果省略依赖，又会埋下 bug。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <hr style=\"border:0;margin:24px 0;height:1px;\">\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">useEffectEvent</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;就是为解决这个痛点而来。它允许你把逻辑放到一个“不会触发依赖更新”的函数里，但依然能拿到最新的 props/state。</span></p>\n      <pre style=\"border-radius:6px 12px 6px 12px;border:1px solid #ebedf0;padding:16px;margin:16px 0;font-size:0.8em;overflow-x:auto;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;line-height:1.6;\" tabindex=\"0\"><code style=\"border:none;padding:0;white-space:nowrap;display:block;\"><span line=\"1\"><span><span leaf=\"\">import</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;useState</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;useEffect</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;useEffectEvent&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;from</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">react</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">;</span></span></span><span line=\"3\"><span><span leaf=\"\">function</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Timer</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">()</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span></span><span line=\"4\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; const</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;[</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">count</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;setCount</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">]</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;=</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;useState</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">0</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">);</span></span></span><span line=\"6\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; const</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;onTick&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">=</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;useEffectEvent</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(()</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;=&gt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span></span><span line=\"7\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; console</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">.</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">log</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">最新 count:</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;count</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">);</span></span></span><span line=\"8\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; });</span></span></span><span line=\"10\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; useEffect</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(()</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;=&gt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span></span><span line=\"11\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; const</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;id&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">=</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;setInterval</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(()</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;=&gt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;onTick</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(),</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;1000</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">);</span></span></span><span line=\"12\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; return</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;()</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;=&gt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;clearInterval</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">id</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">);</span></span></span><span line=\"13\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; },</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;[]);</span></span></span><span line=\"15\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; return</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;(</span></span></span><span line=\"16\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">div</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"17\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">h1</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;{</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">count</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">}&lt;/</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">h1</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"18\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">button</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;onClick</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">={() =&gt;&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">setCount</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">c</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;=&gt;&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">c</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;+&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">1</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">)}&gt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">+1</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&lt;/</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">button</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"19\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">div</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&gt;</span></span></span><span line=\"20\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; );</span></span></span><span line=\"21\"><span><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这样写的好处是：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">定时器只会启动一次；</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">回调里总能拿到最新的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">count</span></code><span leaf=\"\">；</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">不用再小心翼翼地维护依赖数组。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">Performance Tracks：性能调优更直观</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">React 19.2 为 DevTools 带来了新的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">性能轨迹（Performance Tracks）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100052250\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3611111111111111\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"max-width: 100%;border-radius: 8px;margin: 20px auto;display: block;width: auto;height: auto;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=80db24de&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FEO58xpw5UMOt86icUhkTwcOxnuwxzZ4NE4N3m26kcNCzxzEZDd9AZcmwSAickorwMjFMuusHwRbnXm3YTRibhUjrQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 Chrome DevTools 的 Performance 面板里，你现在能直接看到：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">React 的调度与渲染时间线；</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">Suspense 的状态切换。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说，调试性能瓶颈不再是“黑盒子”，你能更清晰地知道到底是哪个组件拖了后腿。</span></p>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">服务端渲染再升级</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次版本也对服务端渲染（SSR）做了几项改进：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">Node.js Web Streams</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">renderToReadableStream</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;等 API 在 Node.js 环境下原生支持 Web Streams，更现代、更高效。</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">cacheSignal</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：能感知缓存生命周期，用于在缓存失效时中断异步操作，例如取消一个不再需要的请求。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <pre style=\"border-radius:6px 12px 6px 12px;border:1px solid #ebedf0;padding:16px;margin:16px 0;font-size:0.8em;overflow-x:auto;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;line-height:1.6;\" tabindex=\"0\"><code style=\"border:none;padding:0;white-space:nowrap;display:block;\"><span line=\"1\"><span><span leaf=\"\">import</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;cache</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;cacheSignal&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">}</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;from</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">react</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">'</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">;</span></span></span><span line=\"3\"><span><span leaf=\"\">const</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;cachedFetch&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">=</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;cache</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">async</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;(</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">url</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">)</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;=&gt;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span></span><span line=\"4\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; const</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;res&nbsp;</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">=</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;await</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;fetch</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">(</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">url</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">,</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;{</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;signal</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">:</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;cacheSignal</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">()</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;});</span></span></span><span line=\"5\"><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; return</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;res</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">.</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">json</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">();</span></span></span><span line=\"6\"><span><span leaf=\"\">});</span></span></span></code></pre>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">部分预渲染</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：先把页面的静态外壳渲染好放到 CDN，等用户访问时再补上动态部分。这能大幅提升首屏加载的速度，结合缓存策略，对大规模站点是非常友好的。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <h2 style=\"margin-top: 16px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.25;display: table;padding: 0.4em 1.4em;margin: 3em auto 1.5em;color: #fff;background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1677ff, #05d4cd);font-size: 1.3em;font-weight: 600;text-align: center;border-radius: 8px 24px 8px 24px;letter-spacing: 0.02em;\"><span leaf=\"\">写在最后</span></h2>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">React 19.2 没有惊天动地的新概念，但它解决了不少日常开发中的痛点：</span></p>\n      <div style=\"margin: 16px 0;background: rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.02);padding: 12px;border-radius: 8px 16px 8px 16px;\">\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">&lt;Activity /&gt;</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;让复杂页面切换时更顺滑，不用担心状态丢失；</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><code style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:#fa2c19;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);font-size:14px;font-family:'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(250, 44, 25, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">useEffectEvent</span></code><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;化解了老生常谈的依赖数组问题；</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 8px;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">性能轨迹（Performance Tracks）让调试不再像摸黑；</span></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.75;color: #4e5969;display: flex;align-items: baseline;margin-bottom: 0;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-right: 10px;color: #fa2c19;background: #fa2c19;border-radius: 0 2px 2px 2px;transform: rotate(45deg) translate(0, -2px);font-size: 8px;font-weight: bold;width: 8px;height: 8px;line-height: 8px;flex-shrink: 0;\"><span leaf=\"\">•</span></p>\n        <p style=\"flex: 1;overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">SSR 的升级也让大规模项目更能跑得动、跑得快。</span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n      <p style=\"padding:0 2px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;line-height:2;margin-bottom:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">如果你的项目里有&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"border-radius:2px;padding:0 2px;font-weight:600;background:rgba(0, 102, 255, 0.1);\"><span leaf=\"\">表单场景多、副作用逻辑复杂，或者依赖 SSR 性能</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，升级到 19.2 能带来不少实打实的好处。</span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "React 19.2 发布了`Activity`组件、`useEffectEvent` Hook、DevTools 性能轨迹及 SSR 增强，旨在优化复杂交互、副作用管理和渲染性能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "React 19.2 发布了`Activity`组件、`useEffectEvent` Hook、DevTools 性能轨迹及 SSR 增强，旨在优化复杂交互、副作用管理和渲染性能。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了 React 19.2 版本带来的几项实用新特性。其中，`<Activity />`组件允许开发者在组件隐藏时保留其状态并暂停更新，极大地简化了路由切换和多标签应用中的状态管理，提升用户体验。`useEffectEvent` Hook 解决了`useEffect`依赖数组导致的重复执行和潜在 bug 问题，使副作用逻辑更清晰和可控。此外，React DevTools 新增了性能轨迹（Performance Tracks），为性能调优提供了更直观的时间线视图。服务端渲染（SSR）方面也得到了升级，包括原生支持 Node.js Web Streams、`cacheSignal`用于缓存生命周期感知，以及部分预渲染功能，显著提升了大规模应用的性能和用户体验。这些改进共同提升了 React 开发的效率和应用性能。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
